Name: Cut
Description: Cut the selection from the document and put it on the Clipboard.

Name: Copy
Description: Copy the selection and put it on the Clipboard.

Name: Font family
Description: Change the font family.

Name: Font size
Description: Change the font size.

Name: Grow font
Description: Increase the font size.

Name: Shrink font
Description: Reduce the font size.

Name: Bold
Description: Change to a heavier font.

Name: Italic
Description: Change to an italic font.

Name: Underline
Description: Draw a line below the text.

Name: Strikethrough
Description: Draw a line through the text.

Name: Subscript
Description: Draw the text smaller and lower than regular text.

Name: Superscript
Description: Draw the text smaller and higher than regular text.

Name: Text color
Description: Change the text color.

Name: Text highlight color
Description: Make text look like it was marked with a highlighter pen.

Name: Decrease indent
Description: Decrease the indent level of the paragraph.

Name: Increase indent
Description: Increase the indent level of the paragraph.

Name: Lists
Description: Click the arrow to choose different list styles.

Name: Change line spacing
Description: Change the spacing between lines of text. Add or remove the space after paragraphs.

Name: Align text left
Description: Align text to the left.

Name: Align text center
Description: Center text.

Name: Align text right
Description: Align text to the right.

Name: Justify text
Description: Align text to both left and right margins adding extra space between words as necessary. This creates a clean look along the left and right side of the page.

Name: Paragraph
Description: Show the Paragraph dialog box.

Name: Picture
Description: Click here for more options such as change picture and resize picture.

Name: Paint drawing
Description: Insert drawing created in Microsoft Paint.

Name: Date and time
Description: Click here for date and time format options.

Name: Insert object
Description: Show the Insert object dialog box.

Name: Find
Description: Find text in the document.

Name: Replace
Description: Replace text in the document.

Name: Paste
Description: Paste the contents of the Clipboard.

Name: Picture
Description: Insert a picture from a file.
Displays the name of the window and contains controls to manipulate it

Name: System
Description: Contains commands to manipulate the window

Name: Minimize
Description: Moves the window out of the way

Name: Restore
Description: Puts a minimized or maximized window back to normal

Name: Close
Description: Closes the window

Name: File tab
Description: Click here to open save or print and to see everything else you can do with your document.

Name: Minimize the Ribbon
Description: Show only the tab names on the Ribbon.

Name: Help
Description: Get help using WordPad.

Name: Save
Description: Save the active document.

Name: Undo
Description: Reverses the last action.

Name: Redo
Description: Repeats the last action.

Name: Paste
Description: Click here for more options such as pasting only plain text.

Name: Zoom out
Description: Zoom out on the document.
Zoom the document to 100% of the normal size.

Name: Ruler
Description: Show or hide ruler. You can use ruler to measure and line up text and objects in the document.

Name: Status bar
Description: Show or hide status bar at the bottom of the window.

Name: Word wrap
Description: Select word wrapping option to change how text appears on your screen. This does not affect how document looks when you print it.

Name: Measurement units
Description: Select measurement units for ruler and page setup.
